      "name": "Spectral Duplicate",
      "type": "feat",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p> The berbalang creates one spectral duplicate of itself in an unoccupied space it can see within 60 feet of it. While the duplicate exists, the berbalang is &amp;Reference[unconscious]{unconscious}. A berbalang can have only one duplicate at a time. The duplicate disappears when it or the berbalang drops to 0 hit points or when the berbalang dismisses it (no action required).</p><p>The duplicate has the same statistics and knowledge as the berbalang, and everything experienced by the duplicate is known by the berbalang. All damage dealt by the duplicate’s attacks is &amp;Reference[psychic]{psychic} damage.</p>\n</section>\nThe [[lookup @name]] uses [[lookup @item.name]].\n</div>",
